N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 5 ยง 103.14 - Rehearing

State Regulations

There shall be no rehearing unless an application is made to
the board therefor, based upon newly discovered evidence which is material and
relevant to the issues presented at the hearing. Notes
